long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_U:
Sync your bookmarks across browsers and devices. Via Nextcloud, or Linkwarden, or any WebDAV service, or any Git service, or Google Drive, end-to-end encrypted, if you want.

More information on https://floccus.org

Support

If you'd like to support the creation and maintenance of this software, you can donate here:
https://floccus.org/donate/

Problems?

Please file bug reports or requests for help over on Github:
https://github.com/floccusaddon/floccus

Legal

Privacy Policy: https://github.com/marcelklehr/floccus/blob/master/PRIVACY_POLICY.md
long.cs:
Synchronizujte své záložky napříč prohlížeči a zařízeními. Prostřednictvím služby Nextcloud, Linkwarden nebo jakékoli služby WebDAV, Git nebo Google Drive, případně šifrované end-to-end.

Další informace na https://floccus.org

https://github.com/floccusaddon/floccus

Zásady ochrany osobních údajů: https://github.com/marcelklehr/floccus/blob/master/PRIVACY_POLICY.md
